      <div id="dbody">
        <div class="Comp" id="descriptionComp">
          <h3>Description {{{auth}}}</h3>
          <p>
            BizBoost Challenge is the first Fizzbiz network Competition ever.
            This competition is for those with small businesses who are aspiring
            to grow their business. The competition is aimed at empowering
            competitors to be innovative, test and improve their marketing
            skills and managerial skills.
          </p>
          <p>
            During the competition, you will be required to grow your business
            followers, likes , orders and increase the interactions between your
            services and products with your customers. The competitors with most
            followers, likes, orders and interactions according to the
            competition phases rules will be declared winners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="Comp" id="reqComp">
          <h3>Requirements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Located in Kenya.
            </li>
            <li>
              Photo copy of National Identification Card (ID) or Driving
              Lincense or Password.
            </li>
            <li>
              Have a Fizzbiz account.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            <strong> <em>Note: </em></strong>
            We encourage competitors to follow and be active in our social media
            platforms to earn extra points.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="Comp" id="rulesComp">
          <h3>Rules</h3>
          <ul class="rulesList">
            <li class="itemList">
              A competitor can only register one business account for the
              competition.
            </li>
            <li class="itemList">
              A business account can only be registered by one competitor.
            </li>
            <li class="itemList">
              The competition will count for real active followers and likes
              only. Detection of any fraud and illegal ways of gaining
              followers, likes and orders will lead to immediate elimination
              from the competition.
            </li>
            <li class="itemList">
              Detection of false orders and checkout will also lead to immediate
              elimination from the competiton.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <strong style="padding: 2%;"><em>Note: </em></strong>
          We encourage competitors to be honest.
        </div>
        <div class="Comp" id="schedComp">
          <h3>Schedule</h3>
          <div>
            <ul class="rulesList">
              <li class="itemList">
                Entrance/ Registration Phase -
                <strong>Feb 1<sup>st</sup> 2024 </strong>
                to
                <strong>March 4<sup>th</sup> 2024 </strong>
              </li>
              <li class="itemList">
                First Selection Phase -
                <strong>March 4<sup>th</sup> 2024 </strong>
                to
                <strong>April 1<sup>st</sup> 2024 </strong>

              </li>
              <li class="itemList">
                Selection Phase -
                <strong>April 1<sup>st</sup> 2024 </strong>
                to
                <strong> May 30<sup>st</sup> 2024 </strong>

              </li>
              <li class="itemList">
                Winners Declaration Phase -
                <strong> May 31<sup>st</sup> 2024 </strong>

              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="Comp">
            <h4 class="scheduleH">
              Entrance Phase Description
            </h4>
            <p class="scheduleP">
              In this phase we allow everyone who has a business account with
              Fizzbiz network to join the competition. There is no age
              limitation to join. After being entered to the competition we
              encourage the competitors to gather and gain more followers, like
              and try to have many orders as possible as these are the criterial
              that we will be using to move forward the successful competitors.
              <br />
              This can be achieved as Fizzbiz network allows business owners to
              share their profiles with their social media links.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="CompSched">
            <h4 class="scheduleH">
              First selection Phase Description
            </h4>
            <p class="scheduleP">
              To be selected for the first selection, any competitors who would
              have gained
              <strong>500 Followers, 100 Likes </strong>
              and had received and checked out at least
              <strong>20 orders</strong>
              will be moved forward with the competition. Your Fizzbiz business
              account should also have an active platform.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="CompSched">
            <h4 class="scheduleH">
              Second Selection Phase Description
            </h4>
            <p class="scheduleP">
              To be selected for the second selection, any competitors who would
              have gained
              <strong>1000 Followers, 500 Likes </strong>
              and had received and checked out at least
              <strong>30 orders</strong>
              will be moved forward with the competition. Your Fizzbiz business
              account should also have an active platform.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="CompSched">
            <h4 class="scheduleH">
              Winners and Prizes
            </h4>
            <p class="scheduleP">
              The Winners of the competition will be the top 10 competitors with
              the highes score. By the end of the second phase the app with the
              highest score will be declare the winner of
              <b><em>KSH 100, 000</em></b>, First runners up will win
              <b><em>KSH 50, 000</em></b>, Second runners up will win
              <b><em>KSH 25, 000</em></b>. For the rest of the 7 competitors,
              they will each win
              <b><em>KSH 5000</em></b>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
